version_description: Now fans from all over the world can download the app, and we fixed various issues users were having. Have fun!

We're back with another update! We took your feedback and spent some time working through the bugs.

Stay tuned for other exciting updates coming this month!

Be sure to keep flash on...

Hey, it’s David!! We’re back, and we’ve got a new name! DISPO.

It’s still super easy to use! Just open the app, take your photos, and wait for them to develop at 9AM the next day. You will get a notification that your photos are developed and ready
